\pard\tx220\tx720\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\sa360\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}Select the documents you wish to merge in the binder.\
{\listtext	2.	}From the main menu, choose 
\f0\fs24 \cf2 <$Scr_Cs::1>
\f2\b Documents > Merge
\f0\b0 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::1>
